+## [2026-07-10T00:00:00Z] feature — local (non-Docker) web install/run mode
+
+**Action:** Added a first-class local install/run mode so the same pipeline is
+reachable from both the TUI and the web UI, sharing one source of truth (the
+user's real XDG/home Hive state via `Hive::Paths`), with the daemon picking up
+tasks by default. The Docker/hivebox path is untouched.
+
+**Code:**
+- `lib/hive/local_preflight.rb` — `Hive::LocalPreflight`: side-effect-free
+  checker (Ruby ≥ 3.4, git, tmux, gh, claude, codex, node/npm, qmd, web
+  bundle, sqlite3) emitting Doctor-style rows + a `hive-local-preflight.v1`
+  envelope. Hive-owned deps are `fixable_by_hive`; external agent CLIs are
+  diagnosed only, with the exact fix command and never a spawned install/login.
+- `lib/hive/web/bundle_installer.rb` + `lib/hive/qmd_bootstrap.rb` — idempotent
+  bootstrap of the deps Hive owns (web `bundle install` + `db:prepare`; qmd via
+  the same intent as `install.sh install_qmd`).
+- `lib/hive/commands/web/service_installer.rb` + `examples/systemd/hive-web.service`
+  + `examples/launchd/local.hive-web.plist` — third subclass of
+  `ServiceInstaller::Base`; `hive web` refactored into a subcommand dispatcher
+  (`run`/`install`/`start`/`stop`/`status`) with bare `hive web` unchanged.
+- `hive web` non-loopback bind guard (refuse unless owner/device-flow,
+  `--unsafe`, or `HIVE_WEB_ALLOW_PUBLIC_BIND`); `Hive::Web::Supervisor` sets the
+  env so the Docker box keeps binding `0.0.0.0`.
+- `lib/hive/daemon_consistency.rb` + `web/app/controllers/daemon_health_controller.rb`
+  + routes — binary-drift detection + owner-gated web repair.
+- `lib/hive/commands/setup.rb` + `hive setup` CLI — orchestrator: bind gate →
+  preflight → bootstrap → daemon install/enroll → web install/start;
+  `hive-setup.v1`; exit 0-with-warnings for external-CLI gaps, non-zero only on
+  hard blockers; idempotent.
+
+**Validation:**
+- `ruby -Itest test/unit/local_preflight_test.rb test/unit/qmd_bootstrap_test.rb`
+- `ruby -Itest test/unit/web/bundle_installer_test.rb test/unit/web/service_installer_test.rb test/unit/web/web_command_test.rb`
+- `ruby -Itest test/unit/daemon_consistency_test.rb test/unit/commands/setup_test.rb`
+- Web integration: `web/test/integration/daemon_health_test.rb` (CI web job).
